rved%20to%20me%20in%20my%20seat%20during%20the%207.5-hour%20flight%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Paris%2C%20I%20liked%20getting%20up%20and%20walking%20over%20to%20the%20pantry%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20bag%20of%20pretzels%2C%20chips%2C%20or%20a%20granola%20bar%20whenever%20I%20felt%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJetBlue%20isn't%20the%20only%20airline%20to%20offer%20a%20perk%20like%20this%2C%20but%20after%20my%20journey%20I%20found%20myself%20wishing%20that%20all%20long-haul%20flights%20had%20self-serve%20snack%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20basket%20of%20snacks%20and%20water%20bottles%20on%20a%20JetBlue%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656df6b40ec98e92f74baa57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20JetBlue%20Pantry%20on%20the%20author's%20long-haul%20international%20flight.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20JetBlue's%20pantry%20service%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Mariya%20Stoyanova%2C%20the%20airline's%20director%20of%20product%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20self-service%20snack%20and%20beverage%20stations%20are%20available%20on%20long-haul%20domestic%20and%20international%20flights%20on%20Airbus%20A321neo%20and%20A321ceo%20aircrafts%2C%20Stoyanova%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20give%20customers%20a%20way%20%26quot%3Bto%20personalize%20their%20travel%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoyanova%20said%20in%20the%20same%20message%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20airline%20is%20implementing%20the%20refreshment%20stations%20on%20its%20Airbus%20A321LR%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20started%20in%202014%2C%20and%20back%20then%20it%20was%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoyanova%20told%20BI.%20She%20said%20there's%20no%20limit%20on%20how%20many%20snacks%20an