for%20his%20sister's%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-doctor-shahana-suicide-her-wedding-cancelled-over-bmw-gold-demand-kerala-doctor-dies-by-suicide-4641245%5C%22%3EJasim%20lost%20his%20sister%20to%20suicide%20this%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fa%3EShe%20was%20upset%20after%20her%20boyfriend%20Dr%20Ruwais%20ES%20called%20off%20the%20wedding%20over%20dowry.%20His%20family%20wanted%20150%20gold%20sovereigns%2C%20a%20BMW%20car%20and%2015%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20but%20Shahana's%20family%20had%20said%20they%20could%20not%20fulfil%20the%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasim%20told%20Mathrubhumi%20that%20it%20was%20Ruwais%20who%20came%20to%20their%20home%20with%20the%20proposal%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20marry%20Shahana.%20%26quot%3BIn%20November%2C%20my%20mother%20and%20I%20visited%20their%20home%20and%20met%20his%20family.%20His%20father%20was%20adamant%20on%20dowry.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20we%20would%20give%20as%20much%20as%20we%20could%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20negotiate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Shahana's%20has%20two%20siblings.%20Her%20father%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20died%20two%20years%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuwais%20and%20Shahana%20were%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20he%20did%20not%20stand%20by%20her%26quot%3B%2C%20Jasim%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20registry%20marriage%2C%20but%20Ruwais%20wanted%20the%20dowry%20demanded%20by%20his%20parents.%20He%20backed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20developments%20broke%20her%20sister%20emotionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasim%20said%20she%20had%20told%20Shahana%20to%20move%20on%2C%20but%20she%20could%20not.%20She%20was%20horrified%20how%20she%20would%20share%20her%20workplace%20with%20Ruwais%20after%20all%20that%20had%20happened%2C%20he%20said.%20This%20Monday%2C%20she%20overdosed%20on%20anaesthesia.%20A%20note%20in%20her%20room%20read%2C