His%20attacks%20included%20a%20jab%20at%20Christie's%20weight%20and%20a%20reference%20to%20a%20past%20scandal%20involving%20Christie's%20allies%2C%20who%20allegedly%20closed%20a%20bridge%20as%20political%20retribution.%20Post-debate%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN%2C%20Christie%20expressed%20his%20exasperation%20with%20Ramaswamy%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20jacka**.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20criticised%20Ramaswamy%20for%20his%20behavior%20towards%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fchris-christie-vivek-ramaswamy-is-a-jacka%2Farticleshow%2F105809612.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K-Pop%20sensation%20Aoora%20to%20enter%20Bigg%20Boss%2017%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701941452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105808921%2Cimgsize-22492.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fbigg-boss-17-k-pop-sensation-aoora-to-enter-salman-khans-show-as-wildcard-says-janam-se-videsi-but-dil-se-ekdum-desi%2Farticleshow%2F105808921.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bigg%20Boss%2017%20prepares%20to%20welcome%20another%20contestant%2C%20Park%20Min-jun%2C%20a%20popular%20South%20Korean%20singer%20and%20composer%20known%20as%20Aoora.%20Aoora%20is%20introduced%20in%20a%20promo%20as%20the%20biggest%20K-pop%20sensation%20and%20expresses%20his%20readiness%20to%20enter%20India's%20biggest%20reality%20show.%20Aoora%20gained%20attention%20in%20India%20for%20his%20unique%20rendition%20of%20Bappi%20Lahiri's%20song%2C%20Jimmy%20Jimmy%2C%20from%20the%20movie%20Disco%20Dancer.%20He%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20South%20Korean%20boy%20band%20Double-A%20and%20its%20subunit%20Aoora%26amp%3BHoik.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Control%20%2B%20All%20or%20Delete%3A%20The%20Draft%20Broadcast%20Bill%20Is%20a%20Blueprint%20for%20Censorship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07144517%2Fmichael-dziedzic-0W4XLGITrHg-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20nearly%20Christmas%2C%20and%20as%20%E2%80%98headlines%20of%20the%20year%E2%80%99%20are%20feted%2C%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20description%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20latest%20censorship%20drive%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetfreedom.in%2Fbroadcast-services-bill-first-read%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Broadcast%20Services%20Bill%20Not%20Looking%20Like%20a%20Wow%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20stand%20on%20the%20podium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20charter%20for%20censorship%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F688072%2Fsiddaramaiah-urgent-steps-special-court-kalburgi-lankesh-murder-trials%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Broadcasting%20Services%20(Regulation)%20Bill%2C%202023%20(Broadcast%20Bill)%3C%2Fa%3E%20drafted%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20(MIB)%20is%20a%20remarkable%20instrument.%20Released%20for%20public%20comment%20on%20November%2011%2C%20this%20is%20an%20omnibus%20set%20of%20rules%20aimed%20at%20shutting%20down%20any%20news%20or%20views%20even%20mildly%20not%20in%20the%20service%20of%20those%20who%20happen%20to%20be%20in%20government.%20Comments%20can%20be%20given%20in%20till%20this%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20enacted%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20see%20how%20any%20future%20government%20would%20want%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20it%20runs%20to%2072%20pages%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20nine%20pages%20that%20the%20Cable%20Television%20Networks%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%201995%C2%A0it%20purportedly%20is%20intended%20to%20replace%2C%20is%20also%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20controlled%20through%20this%3F%20Unlike%20the%20Cable%20TV%20Act%2C%20which%20only%20covered%20broadcasts%20uplinked%20or%20downlinked%20via%20satellite%2C%20the%20Broadcast%20Bill%20includes%20broadcasting%20via%20the%20Internet.%20This%20means%20any%20content%20published%20via%20YouTube%20or%20any%20website%20will%20automatically%20be%20covered.%20Thus%2C%20all%20Over-the-Top%20(OTT)%20content%20and%20digital%20news%20providers%20are%20to%20be%20brought%20under%20government%20oversight.%20But%20who%20else%20exactly%20is%20still%20not%20very%20clear%2C%20and%20not%20because%20unsmart%20people%20have%20drawn%20this%20up.%20Quite%20the%20contrary.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20give%20enough%20room%20in%20the%20clauses%20to%20hustle%20every%20kind%20of%20animal%20into%20the%20tent.%20OTT%2C%20those%20doing%20video%20online%2C%20those%20reposting%20it%2C%20forwarding%20content%20are%20covered%2C%20if%20you%20read%20this%20definition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprogramme%E2%80%9D%20under%20review%20%E2%80%93%20in%20definitions%2C%201%20(dd)%20on%20page%206%20of%20the%20draft%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EProgramme%E2%80%9D%20means%20any%20audio%2C%20visual%20or%20audio-visual%20content%2C%20sign%2C%20signals%2C%20writing%2C%20images%20which%20is%20transmitted%20using%20a%20broadcasting%20network%2C%20and%20includes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(i)%20Exhibition%20of%20films%2C%20features%2C%20dramas%2C%20documentaries%2C%20advertisements%20and%20serials%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(ii)%20Any%20audio%20or%20visual%20or%20audio-visual%20live%20performance%20or%20presentation%20and%20the%20expression%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98programming%20service%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%20shall%20be%20construed%20accordingly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20are%20digital%20websites%20included%20in%20the%20phrase%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwriting%E2%80%9D%3F%20They%20may%20not%2C%20but%20they%20could%20be!%20The%20writing%20is%20suitably%20vague%20to%20not%20be%20restricted%20to%20a%20reference%20to%20just%20captions%20or%20astons%20on%20audio-visual%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cwriting%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20what%20you%20are%20reading%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20least%20wow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20egregious%20over-reach%20in%20the%20draft%20is%20the%20clubbing%20of%20news%20(independent%20news%20websites%2C%20individuals%20now%20established%20as%20popular%20points%20for%20news%20and%20views%2C%20explainer%20videos%2C%20other%20audio-visual%20material%20available%20online)%20with%20OTT%20content%2C%20shows%2C%20serials%2C%20documentaries%20and%20other%20features%20traditionally%20subject%20to%20a%20certification%20norm.%20By%20introducing%20this%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccombo-pack%E2%80%9D%20as%20Jawhar%20Sircar%2C%20an%20ex-CEO%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti%20put%20it%2C%20news%20for%20the%20first%20time%20is%20being%20put%20into%20a%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20or%20CBFC%20inspired%20regime%20reserved%20for%20cinema.%20These%20are%20first%20steps%20to%20establish%20a%20blueprint%20for%20pre-censorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20data%20points%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20692%20million%20mobile%20users%20increasingly%20using%20their%20phones%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F2157%2Finternet-usage-in-india%2F%23dossier-chapter2%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cwatch%20online%20videos%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%2C%20movies%2C%20other%20things%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20%3Cem%3Epull%3C%2Fem%3E%20content%20and%20not%20%3Cem%3Epush%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20like%20TV%20or%20the%20screening%20of%20cinema%20in%20public%20spaces.%20So%20where%20is%20the%20case%20for%20uber-regulation%20of%20this%20medium%3F%20Lawyer%20Nikhil%20Pahwa%20cited%20the%20case%20made%20by%20Mukul%20Rohtagi%20as%20attorney%20general%2C%20for%20the%20government%20not%20wanting%20to%20regulate%20porn%2C%20as%20it%20is%20viewed%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20private%20space%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20become%20a%20totalitarian%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dmukul%2Brohatgi%2Bporn%2Bcensorship%26oq%3Dmukul%2Brohatgi%2Bporn%2Bcensorship%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCDc2NDNqMGoxqAIAsAIA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3Ehe%20told%20the%20court%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20where%20is%20the%20case%20to%20pre-censor%20news%20on%20digital%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20brief%20points%20out%2C%20even%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20CBFC%20regime%2C%20or%20pre-viewing%20certification%20regime%2C%20or%20the%20one%20observed%20by%20cinema%20and%20other%20public%20audio-visual%20material%20goes%2C%20this%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20Shyam%20Benegal%20committee%20from%202016%20had%20suggested%20a%20revamp%20and%20explicitly%20said%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmoral%E2%80%9D%20approach%20to%20censoring%20content%20must%20be%20avoided%2C%20so%20there%20is%20a%20backslide%20on%20that.%20Not%20only%20are%20the%20Benegal%20committee%20ideas%20being%20junked%2C%20news%20is%20being%20pushed%20down%20the%20same%20dark%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20blueprint%20for%20pre-censorship%20and%20censorship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20pre-censorship%20is%20not%20used%20lightly%2C%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98three-tier%E2%80%99%20system%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0the%20so-called%20regulation%20being%20proposed%20%E2%80%93%20ensures%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20government%E2%80%9D%20presence%20at%20all%20tiers%20of%20the%20structure.%20The%20government%20comes%20in%20again%20in%20the%20end%2C%20deciding%20on%20whether%20content%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20down%2C%20news%20persons%20fined%2C%20imprisoned%20or%20if%20devices%20can%20be%20confiscated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20tiers%20proposed%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESelf-regulation%20by%20broadcasters%20and%20broadcasting%20network%20operators%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESelf-regulatory%20organisations%20(SROs)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBroadcast%20Advisory%20Council%20(BAC)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98self-regulation%E2%80%99%20mandates%20each%20broadcaster%2Foperator%20to%20set%20up%20a%20grievance%20redressal%20cell.%20In%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20each%20broadcaster%20must%20have%20a%20Content%20Evaluation%20Committee%20(CEC)%2C%20which%20will%20have%20to%20certify%20all%20material%20going%20out.%20The%20composition%20of%20this%20committee%2C%20its%20size%2C%20quorum%20and%20other%20details%2C%20will%20all%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20government.%20Editorial%20boards%20are%20passe%2C%20clearly%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98committee%E2%80%99%20would%20now%20be%20required%20to%20pre-certify%2C%20for%20example%2C%20whether%20a%20Ravish%20Kumar%20can%20do%20a%20show%20on%20the%20BCCI%20on%20Friday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20all%20broadcasters%2Foperators%20are%20expected%20to%20join%20%E2%80%9CSROs%E2%80%9D%2C%20Clause%2026%20stipulates%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9CSROs%E2%80%9D%20will%20address%20all%20grievances%2C%20appeals%2C%20other%20things%20not%20addressed%20by%20the%20individual%20broadcasters%20and%20issue%20guidelines%2C%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccodes%E2%80%9D%20decided%20by%20the%20government%20(a%20programme%20code%20and%20an%20advertising%20code%2C%20not%20yet%20made%20public).%20Punishment%20can%20mean%20temporary%20suspension%2C%20expulsion%20from%20membership%2C%20advisory%2C%20warning%2C%20censure%2C%20and%2For%20fine%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Backstory%3A%20It's%20Time%20Journalists%20Woke%20Up%20to%20Their%20Digital%20Security%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-its-time-journalists-woke-up-to-their-digital-security%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20Time%20Journalists%20Woke%20Up%20to%20Their%20Digital%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClause%2027%20tells%20us%20how%20the%20Broadcast%20Advisory%20Council%20(BAC)%20will%20be%20set%20up%20and%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20member%20with%2025%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20media%20industry%20will%20function%20as%20the%20chairperson.%20There%20would%20be%20in%20addition%2C%20five%20ex%20officio%20government%20officers%20representing%20the%20MIB%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Social%20Justice%20and%20Empowerment.%20The%20clause%20also%20says%20there%20would%20be%20five%20additional%20%E2%80%9Ceminent%20independent%20persons%E2%80%9D%2C%20all%20central%20government%20appointees.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20terms%20and%20conditions%20related%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20members%20to%20the%20Broadcast%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20the%20manner%20of%20their%20selection%2C%20tenure%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20performance%20of%20their%20functions%20shall%20be%20such%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAC%20shall%20%E2%80%9Chear%20complaints%20regarding%20violation%20or%20contravention%20of%20the%20Programme%20Code%20or%20Advertisement%20Code%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20also%20hear%20appeals%20on%20decisions%20of%20%E2%80%9CSROs%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BAC%20will%20then%20give%20its%20recommendations%20to%20%E2%80%93%20who%20else%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20will%20be%20able%20to%20inspect%2C%20intercept%2C%20monitor%2C%20and%20seize%20the%20equipment%20of%20broadcasting%20networks%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20this%3F%20First%2C%20this%20controversial%20three-tier%20structure%20is%20all%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20of%20dubious%20constitutionality%2C%20and%20is%20not%20being%20based%20upon%20wide%20and%20deep%20public%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20it%20mimics%20what%20the%20controversial%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021%20prescribe.%20These%20have%20been%20challenged%20in%20court%2C%20including%20this%20%E2%80%98three-tier%E2%80%99%20mechanism%2C%20and%20have%20been%20stayed%20by%20at%20least%20two%20high%20courts%2C%20Bombay%20and%20Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20being%20left%20to%20your%20own%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98devices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20of%20deep%20concern%20has%20been%20the%20casual%20snatching%2Fconfiscation%20of%20devices%20of%20journalists%2C%20researchers%20and%20others%20during%20the%20course%20of%20coercive%20police%20action.%20Hash%20values%20are%20often%20not%20given%2C%20police%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20supported%20by%20court%20orders%20or%20even%20warrants.%20This%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20attack%20on%20the%20ability%20of%20a%20free%20press%20to%20function%20and%20has%20been%20done%20with%20increasing%20impunity%20over%20some%20years%20now.%20The%20normalisation%20of%20the%20practice%2C%20and%20for%20hundreds%20of%20journalists%2C%20makes%20stories%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201975%20stopping%20water%20and%20cutting%20electricity%20to%20newspapers%20seem%20like%20a%20dress-rehearsal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20have%20only%20just%20woken%20up%20to%20the%20far-reaching%20implications%20of%20this%20impunity%2C%20and%20on%20November%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20directed%20that%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20by%20five%20academics%20as%20part%20of%20a%20petition%20filed%20in%202021%2C%20be%20circulated%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states.%20On%20November%207%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fproper-guidelines-seizure-of-digital-devices-journalists-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20to%20frame%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20this%20point%2C%20and%20remarked%20that%20uncontrolled%20power%20to%20access%20devices%20of%20journalists%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Five%20renowned%20academics%2C%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20Deepak%20Malghan%20and%20Mukul%20Kesavan%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%20to%20regulate%20the%20search%20of%20electronic%20devices%20by%20agents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20usually%20the%20police.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20hearings%2C%20these%20petitioners%20have%20suggested%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20issued%20as%20directions%20by%20the%20court.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20as%20a%20way%20to%20again%20normalise%20the%20snatching%20of%20devices%20and%20tools%20of%20a%20researcher%20and%20journalist%2C%20Clauses%2031%20onwards%20till%2035%2C%20discuss%20in%20detail%20how%20%E2%80%9Cequipment%E2%80%9D%20of%20said%20broadcasters%2Foperators%20are%20to%20be%20treated.%20Clause%2036(2)%20is%20the%20king%20of%20all%20clauses%20in%20this%20category%2C%20as%20it%20involves%20provision%20for%20blanket%20censorship.%20The%20Union%20government%20gives%20itself%20%E2%80%93%20if%20it%20deems%20it%20necessary%20or%20expedient%20to%20do%20so%20in%20public%20interest%20%E2%80%93%20the%20power%20to%20prohibit%20the%20operation%20of%20any%20broadcasting%20services%20or%20broadcasting%20network%20operators%20in%20the%20areas%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrime-digital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%E2%80%98minimum%20government%2C%20maximum%20governance%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20case%20is%20always%20made%20for%20regulating%20everything.%20So%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20press%20must%20be%20regulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20regulation%20is%20regulation%2C%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20control.%20To%20term%20control%20by%20Union%20government%20as%20%E2%80%98regulation%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20biggest%20typo%20you%20will%20be%20seeing%20this%20year.%20The%20Bill%20has%2060%20places%20where%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cas%20may%20be%20prescribed%E2%80%9D%20features%20and%2017%20times%20when%20%E2%80%9Cas%20notified%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%E2%80%9D%20finds%20a%20place.%20All%20agency%20for%20rule%20making%2C%20which%20will%20further%20restrict%20a%20free%20press%2C%20remains%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20bill%20excludes%20traditional%20newspaper%20%E2%80%98replicas%E2%80%99%20%C2%A0online%20and%20%E2%80%98legacy%E2%80%99%20media%20is%20out%20of%20its%20remit.%20This%20may%20have%20been%20done%20to%20reduce%20the%20noise%20there%20could%20be%20made%20over%20this.%20The%20resistance%20from%20%E2%80%98big%20tech%E2%80%99%20will%20not%20be%20big%20at%20all.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F08%2Findia-twitter-online-censorship%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9C69A%20meetings%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20Twitter%20authorities%20were%20called%20in%20to%20%E2%80%98adhere%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20draconian%2069A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%20and%20pull%20down%20views%20and%20news%20not%20palatable%20to%20the%20central%20government.%20As%20per%20the%20report%2C%20an%20effective%20carrot%20and%20stick%20policy%20is%20in%20place%2C%20which%20%E2%80%98big%20tech%E2%80%99%20is%20happy%20to%20play%20along%20with%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20cash%20tills%20keep%20ringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-s-youtube-journey-15-years-of-global-impact-574427%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%20on%20September%2027%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Csubscribe%20to%20my%20channel%20and%20hit%20the%20Bell%20Icon%20to%20receive%20all%20my%20updates.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20no%20casual%20comment.%20Digital%20is%20vital%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20and%20the%20build%20up%20has%20been%20clear%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20The%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20spend%20on%20digital%20advertising%20has%20rapidly%20outstripped%20that%20on%20print.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemorningcontext.com%2Fchaos%2Fhow-indias-legacy-media-is-losing-out-on-government-ads%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Morning%20Context%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20annual%20reports%20of%20the%20Digital%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20set%20up%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20show%20that%20in%202016-17%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20grant%20to%20MyGov%20was%20Rs%2018.8%20crore.%20In%202017-18%2C%20this%20shot%20up%20to%20Rs%2058.2%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Rs%2058.5%20crore%20in%202018-19%20and%20Rs%2084.88%20crore%20in%202019-20.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%2216%20Indian%20Journalists%20Have%20Been%20Charged%20Under%20UAPA%2C%207%20Are%20Currently%20Behind%20Bars%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2F16-indian-journalists-have-been-charged-under-uapa-7-are-currently-behind-bars%5C%22%3E16%20Indian%20Journalists%20Have%20Been%20Charged%20Under%20UAPA%2C%207%20Are%20Currently%20Behind%20Bars%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20draft%20bill%20is%20a%20clear%20reflection%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20panic%20over%20diversity%20online.%20If%20newspapers%20and%20TV%20channels%20are%20controlled%20by%20restricting%20ads%20or%20giving%20the%20proprietor%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20the%20Broadcast%20Bill%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20formalise%20the%20threat%20of%20punitive%20government%20action%20and%20also%20extend%20its%20reach%20to%20digital%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%202019%20was%20described%20by%20some%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20Whatsapp%20election%E2%80%9D%2C%20then%20this%20one%20appears%20to%20be%20heading%20towards%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20one%20on%20YouTube.%20Digital%20is%20clearly%20the%20big%20cheese%20and%20how%20to%20make%20India%E2%80%99s%20digital%20environment%20as%20monochrome%20as%20the%20one%20on%20television%20(or%20print)%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20problem%20this%20bill%20has%20set%20out%20to%20crack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701941424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07144517%2Fmichael-dziedzic-0W4XLGITrHg-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcontrol-all-or-delete-the-draft-broadcast-bill-is-a-blueprint-for-censorship%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20government%E2%80%9D%20wants%20to%20drag%20independent%20news%20into%20a%20censor%20board%20framework.%20No%20independent%20regulation%20is%20proposed.%20The%20government%20is%20everywhere%20and%20in%20control.%20The%20dubious%20%E2%80%983-tier%E2%80%99%20regulatory%20structure%20proposed%20is%20recycled%20out%20of%20IT%20Rules%202021%2C%20which%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20two%20high%20courts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcontrol-all-or-delete-the-draft-broadcast-bill-is-a-blueprint-for-censorship%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Special%20Court%20May%20Be%20Set%20Up%20For%20Kalburgi%2C%20Gauri%20Lankesh%20Murder%20Trials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F26183509%2Flankesh-kalburgi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20directed%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20home%20secretary%20on%20Wednesday%20(December%206)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-orders-setting-up-of-special-courts-for-lankesh-kalburgi-trials-101701890075440.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ctake%20urgent%20steps%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20expedite%20the%20trials%20in%20the%20M.M.%20Kalburgi%20and%20Gauri%20Lankesh%20murder%20cases%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-cm-orders-setting-up-special-courts-for-trial-in-killings-of-writer-mm-kalburgi-journalist-gauri-gowri-lankesh%2Farticle67610420.ece%5C%22%3EA%20special%20court%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20set%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20try%20both%20cases%20together%2C%20given%20that%20they%20involve%20common%20accused%20persons%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalburgi%2C%20a%20Kannada%20author%20and%20rationalist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-34105187%5C%22%3Ewas%20shot%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20his%20Dharwad%20home%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELankesh%20was%20a%20journalist-activist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgauri-lankesh-noted-journalist-dissenter-shot-dead-bangalore%5C%22%3Eshot%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20her%20Bengaluru%20home%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalburgi%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Umadevi%20and%20Lankesh%E2%80%99s%20sister%20Kavitha%20reportedly%20wrote%20to%20Siddaramaiah%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20investigation%20into%20their%20relatives%E2%80%99%20murders%20and%20requested%20that%20a%20special%20court%20be%20set%20up%20to%20hear%20the%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0as%20asking%20the%20home%20secretary%20to%20take%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20steps%E2%80%9D%20with%20regard%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20special%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fgauri-lankesh-was-killed-for-being-anti-hindu-confession-of-main-accused-naveen-kumar%2F68052%2F%5C%22%3Ekilled%20because%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20from%20Karnataka%20reportedly%20said%20in%20a%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20her%20death%2C%20Lankesh%E2%80%99s%20weekly%20magazine%20had%20come%20under%20attack%20for%20her%20views%20against%20the%20communal%20politics%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20%E2%80%98Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20a%20man%20who%20confessed%20to%20killing%20Lankesh%20said%20he%20was%20told%20to%20do%20so%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fi-killed-gauri-lankesh-to-save-my-religion-waghmore-to-sit%2Farticleshow%2F64608133.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Csave%20his%20religion%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20six%20out%20of%20143%20witnesses%20in%20Kalburgi%E2%80%99s%20case%20and%2097%20out%20of%20530%20witnesses%20in%20Lankesh%E2%80%99s%20case%20have%20been%20examined%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20regard%20to%20Lankesh%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20state%20home%20secretary%20that%20the%20SIT%20has%20arrested%2018%20people%20so%20far%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20court%20had%20started%20the%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20in%20July%202022%2C%20the%20case%20is%20progressing%20at%20a%20slow%20pace%20due%20to%20other%20cases%20pending%20before%20the%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reportedly%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%E2%80%99s%202018%20chargesheet%20reportedly%20also%20said%20that%20two%20others%20%E2%80%93%20rationalists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlwNe7r6C6NM%5