0that%20will%20people%20with%20Androids%20to%20use%20iMessage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20means%20Android%20users%20can%20send%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-no-incentive-change-green-bubbles-android-blue-texts-iphones-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblue-bubble%20texts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20voice%20messages%2C%20and%20reactions%20to%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20prototype%20was%20made%20by%20a%20teen%20who%20said%20he%20had%20reverse-engineered%20iMessage%2C%20the%20app's%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20dreaded%20green%20bubble%20text%20messages%20are%20the%20only%20thing%20stopping%20you%20from%20making%20the%20switch%20over%20to%20Android%2C%20today%20could%20be%20your%20lucky%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%2C%20unofficial%20iMessage%20app%20for%20Android%20is%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beeper.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeeper%20Mini%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20Android%20app%20%E2%80%94%20not%20affiliated%20with%20Apple%20in%20any%20way%20%E2%80%94%20that%20lets%20you%20send%20blue-bubble%20text%20messages%20that%20were%20previously%20only%20available%20to%20Apple%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20says%20the%20app%20also%20allows%20you%20to%20access%20features%20that%20were%20previously%20only%20available%20on%20iMessage%20and%20iPhone%2C%20like%20Apple's%20read%20receipts%2C%20full-resolution%20picture%20and%20video%20attachments%2C%20emoji%20reactions%2C%20voice%20messages%2C%20and%20stickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20photos%20of%20the%20interface%20of%20the%20Beeper%20Mini%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570cfa20ec98e92f74cd97c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221787%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20used%20to%20be%20impossible%20to%20get%20iMessage%20on%20a%20non-Apple%20device%2C%20but%20a%20new%20app%20could%20change%20everything.%3Cp%3EBeeper%20Mini%2FGoogle%20Play%20Store%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20bound%20to%20annoy%20Apple%2C%20which%20is%20fiercely%20protective%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-imessage-on-android-would-hurt-more-than-help-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiMessage%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20the%20coveted%20blue-bubble%20texts%20are%20a%20key%20way%20the%20iPhone%20company%20keeps%20people%20locked%20into%20its%20product%20ecosystem.%20So%20while%20the%20app%20is%20available%20for%20download%20on%20the%20Google%20Play%20store%20now%2C%20don't%20be%20surprised%20if%20Apple%20tries%20to%20intervene%20and%20get%20it%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20requires%20a%20%241.99%20monthly%20subscription.%20Beeper%20Mini%20cofounder%20Eric%20Migicovsky%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20fee%20is%20to%20show%20that%20it's%20a%20trustworthy%20service%20and%20keeps%20it%20free%20of%20ads.%20The%20company%20won't%20sell%20or%20upload%20your%20data%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20says%20the%20app%20will%20connect%20your%20Android%20phone%20to%20Apple%20servers%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20send%20and%20receive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fend-to-end-encryption%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend-to-end%20encrypted%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20doesn't%20read%20your%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prototype%20for%20the%20app%20came%20from%20a%20surprising%20source%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20created%20by%20a%2016-year-old%20student%2C%20according%20to%20Migicovsky.%20The%20teenager%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20over%20Discord%20last%20summer%20and%20said%20he%20had%20reverse-engineered%20iMessage%2C%20which%20had%20never%20been%20done%20before%2C%20according%20to%20Migicovsky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeeper%20isn't%20technically%20the%20first%20Android%20app%20to%20offer%20the