%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchie%2C%20son%20of%20the%20owner%20of%20Riverdale's%20only%20travel%20agency%2C%20has%20such%20faith%20in%20his%20own%20aura%20that%20he%20presumes%20that%20neither%20of%20the%20two%20girls%20will%20have%20any%20problem%20with%20his%20habitual%20two-timing.%20This%20may%20be%201964%20but%20Veronica%20and%20Betty%20are%20'modern'%20and%20tough%20young%20women%20who%20value%20their%20friendship%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20knows%20when%20and%20how%20to%20assert%20their%20agency%20despite%20their%20hearts%20being%20expectedly%20prone%20to%20possessiveness%2C%20envy%20and%20sorrow.%20Their%20strong%20bonding%20faces%20its%20share%20of%20up%20and%20downs.%20How%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20reverses%20forms%20an%20important%20part%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20girl%20in%20their%20gang%2C%20Ethel%20Muggs%20(Dot.)%2C%20is%20the%20very%20best%20at%20what%20she%20does%20-%20she%20is%20a%20much%20sought-after%20hairstylist.%20Her%20allegiance%20to%20her%20employer%2C%20Pam%20(Delnaaz%20Irani)%2C%20is%20tested%20when%20a%20new%20salon%20with%20imported%2C%20state-of-the-art%20equipment%20opens%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20for%20a%20moment%20do%20the%20three%20leads%20seem%20to%20be%20raw%20as%20actors.%20They%20deliver%20the%20goods%20with%20remarkable%20elan.%20No%20less%20impressive%20are%20the%20actors%20who%20complete%20the%20young%20cast%20that%20fleshes%20out%20Archie%20Comics%20characters%20with%20distinct%20individual%20traits%20without%20letting%20any%20of%20them%20sink%20into%20predictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVedang%20Raina%20as%20Reggie%20Mantle%2C%20Mihir%20Ahuja%20as%20Jughead%20and%20Yuvraj%20Menda%20as%20the%20nerdy%2C%20self-effacing%20Dilton%20Doiley%20(who%20proves%20his%20worth%20when%20it%20really%20matters)%20sail%20through%20their%20roles%20with%20utmost%20ease.%20The%20script%20is%20their%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20mixes%20spoken%20dialogues%20with%20a%20slew%20of%20songs%20that%20provide%20clear%20glimpses%20into%20volatile%20minds%20as%20the%20bubbly%20teenagers%20make%20their%20ways%20through%20a%20crucial%20phase%20of%20their%20lives%20that%20sees%20them%20transition%20to%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20the%20characters%20and%20their%20city%20remain%20unchanged%20in%20The%20Archies%20but%20everything%20else%20in%20the%20Netflix%20film%20directed%20by%20Zoya%20Akhtar%20and%20written%20by%20her%20with%20Reema%20Kagti%20and%20Ayesha%20DeVitre%20Dhillon%20is%20given%20lively%20new%20trappings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20glaring%20disconnect%20between%20what%20the%20comics%20are%20-%20an%20American%20pop%20culture%20phenomenon%20(that%20had%20huge%20currency%20on%20the%20subcontinent%20especially%20in%20the%201960s%20and%201970s)%20-%20and%20the%20delightfully%20cheerful%20fable%20about%20a%20community%20with%20deep%20roots%20in%20India's%20colonial%20past%20and%20yet%20wholly%20committed%2C%20post-Independence%2C%20to%20the%20land%20of%20their%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freshness%20of%20the%20brew%20that%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%20rustles%20up%20rests%20primarily%20on%20the%20flamboyant%20and%20fastidious%20visual%20design%20and%20the%20flourish%20that%20the%20principal%20actors%20impart%20to%20the%20film%2C%20which%20addresses%20the%20pangs%20of%20growing%20up%20and%20standing%20up%20for%20a%20cause%20while%20it%20tackles%20the%20larger%20themes%20of%20corporate%20greed%2C%20media%20freedom%20and%20the%20scourge%20of%20unsustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20striking%20aspect%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20blends%20the%20flip%20(not%20flimsy)%20with%20the%20solemn%20(not%20self-conscious)%20as%20a%20group%20of%20teenagers%20deal%20with%20each%20other's%20angularities%2C%20their%20parents'%20desires%2C%20and%20the%20impositions%20of%20powerful%20people%20bent%20upon%20robbing%20their%20city%20of%20something%20its%20denizens%20hold%20dear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20celebrates%20the%20restless%2C%20kinetic%20spirit%20of%20the%20young%20even%20as%20it%20skewers%20the%20skullduggery%20that%20is%20afoot%20in%20the%20name%20of%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20town%20square%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20shopping%20plaza%20and%20a%20grand%20hotel%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20Riverdale's%20tourism%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20council%20head%20Dawson%20(Vinay%20Pathak)%20is%20in%20cahoots%20with%20entrepreneur%20Hiram%20Lodge%20(Ally%20Khan)%2C%20Veronica's%20ever-busy%2C%20profit-obsessed%20father.%20The%20two%20men%20manipulate%20the%20council%20members%20to%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20Green%20Park%2C%20a%20space%20where%20the%20city's%20roots%20literally%20lie%2C%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20construction%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20just%20live%20your%20life%20for%20kicks%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Riverdale%20High%20students%20croon%20when%20Archie%20says%20he%20has%20no%20interest%20in%20politics.%20He%20plans%20to%20fly%20away%20to%20London%20to%20study%20even%20though%20his%20parents%20aren't%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20idea.%20Betty%2C%20Reggie%2C%20Jughead%2C%20Ethel%20and%20Dilton%20have%20no%20such%20escape%20route.%20They%20have%20far%20too%20much%20at%20stake%20to%20turn%20their%20backs%20on%20the%20fate%20of%20Riverdale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetty's%20father%20stands%20to%20lose%20his%20book%20shop%20and%20Reggie'e%20editor-dad%20is%20determined%20to%20protect%20his%20newspaper's%20freedom.%20Riverdale's%20best-loved%20spots%20-%20Suzie's%20flower%20shop%2C%20Pop%20Tate's%20cafe%20and%20Pam's%20beauty%20salon%20are%20among%20them%20-%20face%20closure%20as%20Hiram%20Lodge%20proposes%20to%20buy%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeronica's%20dad%20is%20the%20man%20responsible%20for%20the%20threat%20looming%20over%20the%20small%20businesses%20-%20a%20fact%20that%20causes%20frictions%20serious%20enough%20to%20nearly%20drive%20a%20wedge%20between%20her%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Riverdale%20High%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20precious%20in%20Riverdale%20than%20the%20park%20and%20its%20trees%20-%20each%20one%20of%20them%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell%20because%20they%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20city's%20landscape%20and%20history.%20They%20are%20worth%20fighting%20for.%20Once%20that%20realisation%20dawns%20on%20Archie%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20close%20ranks%20and%20start%20a%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F07zwmOypaV8%3Fsi%3DsxkI9wOHibvSLUet%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20setting%20the%20story%20in%20a%20community%20that%20chose%20India%20and%20by%20opting%20for%20the%20years%201947%20and%201964%20as%20the%20two%20chronological%20bookends%20of%20the%20narrative%2C%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20clearly%20seeking%20to%20convey%20much%20more%20than%20what%20the%20encounters%20that%20shape%20a%20crucial%20year%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20Riverdale%20youngsters%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20attainment%20of%20Independence%20and%20the%20death%20of%20its%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20-%20neither%20of%20the%20two%20signposts%20of%20Indian%20history%20is%20specifically%20mentioned%20-%20were%20separated%20by%2017%20years.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20age%20of%20the%20younger%20characters%20in%20the%20film.%20They%20are%20as%20old%20as%20the%20free%20nation%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20indeed%20politics.%20Even%20when%20life%20is%20awash%20with%20colours%2C%20songs%2C%20dances%20and%20the%20elixir%20of%20youth%20the%20way%20it%20is%20in%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Arc