%20to%20get%20his%20loyalists%20tickets%2C%20knowing%20well%20that%20he%20would%20not%20get%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20if%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20support%20of%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20MLAs.%20This%20worked%20well%20for%20him%20and%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20upset%20the%20apple%20cart%2C%20endorsed%20Mr%20Reddy's%20claim%20to%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20faces%20the%20tall%20challenge%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20Congress's%20poll%20guarantees%20and%20preparing%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20due%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701937320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foohhrj7o_revanth-reddy_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-gandhis-attend-swearing-in-ceremony-4641721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anumula%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20chief%20of%20Telangana%20Congress%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20party's%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20November%2030%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20was%20today%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20state's%20second%20Chief%20Minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-gandhis-attend-swearing-in-ceremony-4641721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-gandhis-attend-swearing-in-ceremony-4641721%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-takes-oath-as-telangana-chief-minister-gandhis-attend-swearing-in-ceremony-4641721%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Naga%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Sneaking%20Out%20Is%20Not%20for%20Good%20Saudi%20Girls%20in%20Ov