C%20and%20displaced%20in%20Palestine.%20I%20attach%20human%20faces%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Ramallah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20will%20not%20pretend%20to%20write%20from%20a%20neutral%20and%20distanced%20position%20today.%20Neutrality%20often%20helps%20the%20oppressor%2C%20not%20the%20oppressed.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Palestine%20has%20become%20as%20far%20and%20as%20close%20as%20India%2C%20in%20some%20ways.%20When%20I%20read%20the%20news%20from%20Gaza%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20hits%20me%20as%20if%20something%20horrible%20is%20unfolding%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20destruction%20of%20Gaza%20has%20shaken%20the%20world%20to%20the%20core.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20including%2010%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza.%20Another%2017%2C00%2C000%20people%20stand%20displaced.%20Numbers%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this.%20Hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20universities%2C%20homes%2C%20refugee%20shelters%20and%20UN%20offices%20have%20been%20relentlessly%20bombed.%20A%20senior%20UN%20human%20rights%20expert%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F31%2Fun-official-resigns-israel-hamas-war-palestine-new-york%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Gaza%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%20Along%20with%20Gaza%2C%20all%20the%20rules%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20have%20been%20bombed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces.%20Amidst%20this%20destruction%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20for%20liberation%20has%20found%20renewed%20support%20across%20the%20globe.%20Millions%20have%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Berlin%2C%20Paris%2C%20Cairo%2C%20Amman%2C%20Stockholm%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%20Seoul%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%20Wellington%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Islamabad%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Sao%20Paulo%2C%20Bogota%2C%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Santiago%20and%20countless%20ot