e%20chiefs%20of%20various%20state%20units.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frevanth-reddy-telangana-chief-minister-congress-revanth-reddy-the-new-telangana-chief-minister-who-had-egg-thrown-at-him-4636632%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevanth%20Reddy%3A%20Next%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Once%20Had%20Egg%20Thrown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Gaddam%20Prasad%20Kumar%2C%20who%20beat%20Anand%20Methuku%20of%20the%20outgoing%20BRS%20and%20trounced%20P%20Naveen%20Kumar%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20win%20the%20Vicarabad%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20will%20be%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWho%20Are%20The%2012%20To%20Take%20Oath%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20the%20incoming%20ministers%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Also%20in%20the%20(short-lived)%20race%20to%20become%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Vikramarka%20is%20a%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20outgoing%20Assembly.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Mala%20community%2C%20listed%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20he%20delivered%2011%20of%2012%20seats%20in%20the%20state's%20Khammam%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20efforts%20for%20the%20Congress'%20win%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20four-month%20padyatra%2C%20or%20foot%20march%2C%20that%20covered%20nearly%201%2C370%20km.%20Mr%20Reddy%20won%20the%20Madhira%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20has%20held%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20third%20Congress%20leader%20in%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20race%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20is%20a%20party%20loyalist%20and%20former%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20to%20boot.%20Now%20a%20seven-time%20election-winner%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20was%20also%20boss%20of%20the%20party's%20state%20unit%20before%20he%20was%20replaced%20with%20Revanth%20Reddy%2