C%20listed%20as%20a%20Backward%20Class%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Husnabad%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKomatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yet%20another%20veteran%20-%20with%20over%20three%20decades%20in%20the%20party%20-%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20another%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20who%20was%20fielded%20in%20this%20election%20and%20who%20has%20resigned%20in%20order%20to%20become%20a%20Telangana%20minister.%20And%2C%20like%20Mr%20Vikramarka%2C%20he%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20Congress%20swept%20his%20district%20-%20the%20party%20won%2011%20of%2012%20seats%20in%20Nalgonda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20won%20the%20Nalgonda%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20won%20thrice%20between%201999%20and%202009%20before%20being%20beaten%20decisively%20by%20the%20BRS'%20KB%20Reddy%20in%202018.%20He%20won%20the%20seat%20back%20from%20his%20rival%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDamodar%20Raja%20Narasimha%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20(undivided)%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Narasimha%20was%20also%20Minister%20of%20Higher%20Education%20and%20Agriculture.%20A%20Dalit%20from%20Telangana's%20Medak%20area%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Andole%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20recovering%20it%20from%20the%20BRS%20that%20won%20it%20in%20two%20previous%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPonguleti%20Srinivas%20Reddy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Elected%20to%20the%20Khammam%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202014%2C%20on%20a%20ticket%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BRS%20in%202018%20and%20the%20Congress%20just%20before%20this%20election.%20Called%20the%20'strongman'%20of%20the%20district%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Palairu%20seat%20by%20over%2056%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDana%20Anasuya%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Popularly%20called%20Seethakka%2C%20Ms%20Anasuya%20is%20a%20member%20of%20a%20tribal%20community%20from%20Mulugu%20district%20and%20is%20fondly%20referred%20to