2%3A%22Many%20parts%20of%20Chennai%20city%20are%20still%20water-logged%20after%20torrential%20rains%20ahead%20of%20a%20severe%20cyclone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67645286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67645286.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67645286.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Excerpt%3A%20Why%20India's%20Social%20Development%20Indicators%20Lag%20Behind%20its%20Neighbours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07112307%2Ffd42a93e-1b05-4602-adbc-827125ca5f01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EUNEQUAL%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%20%3Cem%3Eby%20writer%20and%20activist%20Swati%20Narayan%2C%20published%20by%20Westland%20on%20November%2027%2C%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20centre%20was%20a%20joke.%20The%20only%20living%20beings%20on%20the%20premises%20were%20grazing%20in%20the%20courtyard.%20%E2%80%98The%20sacred%20cows%20are%20the%20doctors%2C%E2%80%99%20laughed%20my%20research%20coordinator%2C%20Ismael.%20The%20entire%20building%20was%20dilapidated%E2%80%94floors%20broken%2C%20walls%20collapsing%2C%20paint%20peeling%20and%20weeds%20growing%20in%20the%20rooms%20and%20roof.%20In%20the%20village%20we%20were%20visiting%2C%20this%20was%20the%20only%20health%20centre%20within%20a%20kilometre%20radius.%20The%20doctors%20and%20health%20workers%20had%20obviously%20abandoned%20this%20workplace%20despite%20continuing%20to%20draw%20a%20hefty%20government%20salary.%20The%20only%20other%20health%20facility%20was%20more%20than%2014%20kilometres%20away.%20Bihar%20does%20have%20better%20health%20centres.%20But%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Kishanganj%20district%2C%20most%20government%20services%20we%20saw%20were%20similarly%20in%20shambles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20went%20to%20the%20homes%20of%20two%20accredited%20social%20health%20activists%20(ASHAs)%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20village%20as%20doorstep%20health%20workers.%20Neither%20of%20them%20had%20received%20any%20medicines%20for%20two%20years%20and%20we%20heard%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints.%20Their%20kits%20only%20had%20old%20oral%20rehydration%20salt%20(ORS)%20packets%20and%20a%20few%20government%20brands%20of%20condoms%20and%20contraceptive%20pills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20323px)%2085vw%2C%20323px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22323%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2.jpg%20793w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2-198x300.jpg%20198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07101333%2Funnamed-2-677x1024.jpg%20677w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22489%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESwati%20Narayan%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EUNEQUAL%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EWestland%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20even%20more%20shocked%20when%20I%20walked%20up%20to%20a%20neighbouring%20house.%20Peeping%20through%20the%20window%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20severely%20disabled%20boy%20huddled%20inside%20a%20dark%20room.%20I%20was%20heartbroken%20to%20find%20that%20he%20had%20been%20kept%20hidden%20away%20like%20this.%20His%20mother%2C%20with%20teary%20eyes%2C%20asked%20us%20if%20we%20could%20help%20in%20any%20way.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20had%20to%20tell%20her%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20were%20medical%20practitioners%20but%20that%20we%20would%20love%20to%20speak%20to%20her%20son.%20When%20Bhim%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20courtyard%2C%20he%20flashed%20an%20unforgettable%20smile.%20I%20impressed%20upon%20his%20mother%20that%2C%20ideally%2C%20he%20should%20be%20exposed%20to%20some%20sunlight%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhim%E2%80%99s%20unspeakably%20poor%20parents%20were%20at%20their%20wit%E2%80%99s%20end.%20There%20was%20no%20healthcare%20facility%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20They%20loved%20their%20son%2C%20but%20simply%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20for%20him.%20I%20felt%20just%20as%20helpless.%20On%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20stand%20together%20for%20family%20photo.%20Later%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20print%20the%20grainy%20image%20along%20with%20a%20disability%20pension%20form%20to%20hand%20over%20to%20Bhim%E2%80%99s%20mother.%20But%20I%20knew%20fully%20well%20that%2C%20at%20best%2C%20these%20were%20only%20symbolic%20gestures%20of%20comfort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20just%20one%20home.%20During%20our%20survey%20in%20Bihar%2C%20we%20met%20many%20families%20in%20similar%20or%20even%20worse%20predicaments%2C%20struggling%20with%20chronic%20ailments.%20They%20wage%20a%20daily%20battle%20against%20the%20criminal%20neglect%20of%20public%20healthcare%20in%20India.%20The%20poorest%20families%20pay%20the%20indescribably%20heaviest%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reach%20this%20distant%20village%2C%20we%20had%20crossed%20a%20river%20on%20a%20precarious%20boat%20that%20two%20men%20somehow%20rowed%20using%20only%20bamboo%20poles.%20The%20narrow%20deck%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Edinghy%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20packed%20with%20fifteen-odd%20bicycles%20and%20a%20few%20motorcycles%20(including%20our%20own).%20A%20bevy%20of%20weary%20villagers%20with%20their%20jute%20sacks%2C%20chickens%20and%20household%20wares%20had%20jostled%20for%20space.%20It%20was%20a%20miracle%20we%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20toppled%20over.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20monsoon%2C%20such%20rickety%20boats%20were%20the%20primary%20means%20of%20transport%20across%20the%20flooded%20plains%20of%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETravelling%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%20of%20Nepal%20was%20equally%20tricky.%20One%20of%20the%20randomly%20selected%20villages%20for%20my%20survey%20was%20said%20to%20be%20three%20hours%20away%20from%20the%20district%20headquarters.%20But%20the%20journey%20ultimately%20took%20seven%20hours.%20After%20two%20hours%20on%20the%20rickety%20bus%2C%20we%20came%20across%20the%20raging%20Kamlamai%20river%2C%20which%20had%20flooded%20due%20to%20the%20rains.%20The%20veteran%20driver%20calmly%20stopped%20the%20bus%20midstream.%20Two%20conductors%20stepped%20out%20and%2C%20walking%20with%20meditative%20steps%20in%20the%20rushing%20current%2C%20surveyed%20the%20riverbed.%20After%20three%20hours%20of%20these%20rudimentary%20explorations%2C%20the%20driver%20finally%20figured%20out%20the%20best%20route%20to%20navigate%20the%20bus%20across%20the%20river.%20As%20passengers%20stuck%20inside%2C%20we%20had%20our%20stomachs%20in%20knots.%20Finally%2C%20when%20the%20bus%20reached%20the%20shore%2C%20all%20of%20us%20broke%20into%20a%20spontaneous%20round%20of%20claps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20perilous%20terrain%2C%20this%20far-removed%20Nepali%20village%20had%20relatively%20good%20healthcare%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20Bihar%20next%20door.%20When%20I%20suffered%20a%20sudden%20bout%20of%20severe%20vertigo%2C%20my%20Nepali%20translator%20Bijeta%20literally%20saved%20my%20life.%20The%20private%20pharmacy%20she%20took%20me%20to%20was%20a%20blessing%2C%20even%20with%20its%20limited%20stock%20of%20medicines.%20The%20shop%20even%20had%20beds%20in%20a%20room%20at%20the%20back%20to%20administer%20saline%20drips%20to%20patients.%20Later%2C%20when%20we%20finally%20reached%20the%20well-stocked%20government%20clinic%20an%20hour%20away%2C%20we%20met%20the%20health%20worker%20Gopal.%20Though%20he%20was%20not%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20had%2017%20years%20of%20experience%20under%20his%20belt.%20Gopal%20used%20his%20stethoscope%20and%20blood%20pressure%20instrument%20to%20check%20my%20extremely%20low%20BP.%20Both%20his%20medical%20skills%20and%20endearing%20pidgin%20English%20lifted%20our%20spirits%20instantly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20health%20posts%20in%20Nepal%20are%20also%20managed%20by%20junior%20doctors.%20Unlike%20India%2C%20the%20Nepali%20government%20insists%20that%20all%20private%20medical%20colleges%20offer%20some%20students%20free%20education%20with%20full%20scholarship.%20After%20completion%20of%20their%20degrees%2C%20these%20young%20doctors%20have%20to%20serve%20in%20rural%20areas%20as%20a%20part%20of%20their%20two-year%20mandatory%20government%20service%20bond.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%C2%A0Unequal%3A%20Why%20India%20Lags%20Behind%20Its%20Neighbours%2C%C2%A0Swati%20Narayan%2C%20Westland%20Books%2C%20Context%20Imprint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESwati%20Narayan%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20activist.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20and%20Human%20Development%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701934252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07112307%2Ffd42a93e-1b05-4602-adbc-827125ca5f01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fexcerpt-why-indias-social-development-indicators-lag-behind-its-neighbours%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swati%20Narayan's%20'UNEQUAL'%20offers%20a%20comparison%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20development%20indicators%20with%20that%20of%20its%20South%20Asian%20neighbours%20and%20an%20immersive%20examination%20of%