e%20or%20hazardous%20pollution%20only%20when%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20comes%20forth%20with%20its%20knee-jerk%20reaction%2C%20its%20typical%20way%20of%20dealing%20with%20any%20persistent%20problem.%20Close%20the%20schools%3B%20apply%20odd-even%20car%20driving%20on%20alternate%20days%3B%20stop%20construction%20activity%20on%20and%20off%2C%20etc.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20the%20high%20AQI%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fat-3230-punjab-records-maximum-farm-fires-in-a-day-air-quality-severe-in-parts-of-haryana%2Farticleshow%2F104990953.cms%5C%22%3Eburning%20of%20stubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20prefers%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20it%2C%20though%20the%20same%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20heads%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20city%20slicks%20know%20this%20much%20about%20rural%20India%20that%20after%20harvesting%20and%20cutting%20paddy%2C%20the%20farmer%20burns%20the%20remaining%20stubble.%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20always%20fathom%20why.%20A%20bewildered%20city%20boy%20said%20to%20me%2C%20stubble%20has%20been%20there%20for%20centuries%2C%20why%20do%20farmers%20burn%20it%20now%3F%20Dear%20innocent%2C%20the%20practice%20started%20when%20mechanised%20cutting%20replaced%20manual%20cutting%20of%20paddy%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20advent%20of%20green%20revolution.%20With%20mechanised%20cutting%2C%20the%20stubble%20is%20cut%20so%20fine%20that%20it%20does%20not%20retain%20the%20juice%20or%20the%20texture%20to%20be%20suitable%20for%20fodder%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20manual%20cutting.%20No%20longer%20of%20any%20use%20to%20the%20farmer%2C%20he%20burns%20the%20stubble%20to%20free%20the%20field%20for%20other%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20solution%2C%20and%20indeed%20a%20productive%20one%2C%20is%20to%20turn%20the%20stubble%20into%20manure.%20One%20available%20solution%20now%20is%20to%20add%20the%20IARI-developed%20Pusa%20bio%20dispenser%20to%20the%20hard%20stubble.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fungi-based%20liquid%20solution%20with%20the%20proclivity%20to%20soften%20it%20so%20that%20the%20resultant%20mix%20can%20be%20spread%20on%20the%20soil%20as%20manure.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20we%20expect%20the%20farmers%20to%20buy%20the%20capsules.%20They%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20incur%20the%20expense%2C%20or%20undertake%20the%20laborious%20process%20of%20mixing%20it%20with%20the%20soil.%20They%20are%20not%20convinced%20of%20its%20efficacy%20or%20its%20cost-effectiveness.%20Random%20media%20promotion%20and%20government%20prodding%20have%20failed%20to%20motivate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20routinely%20resorts%20to%20banning%20stubble%20burning.%20We%20know%20that%20legal%20bans%20are%20ineffective%20in%20our%20corruption-prone%20society.%20All%20that%20happens%20is%20that%20the%20authority%20in%20charge%20makes%20money%20from%20bribes%20while%20the%20law%20is%20trashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20the%20only%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20burning%20issue%20is%20to%20treat%20it%20as%20a%20policy%20matter%2C%20similar%20to%20building%20roads%20and%20bridges%20or%20policing%20and%20defence.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20price%20is%20paid%20by%20the%20general%20public%20through%20compromised%20health%20and%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20through%20a%20multi-pronged%20and%20well-planned%20policy.%20One%20potential%20solution%20could%20involve%20purchasing%20stubble%20from%20farmers%20and%20storing%20it%20at%20nearby%20manned%20centres.%20The%20establishment%20of%20numerous%20collection%20and%20storage%20centres%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20farms%20would%20be%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnologies%20such%20as%20the%20Pusa%20dispenser%20or%20any%20new%20materials%20resulting%20from%20future%20research%20could%20then%20be%2