msid-105796501%2Cimgsize-34360.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fsmoked-out-gang-that-supplied-clean-weed%2Farticleshow%2F105796442.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch%20busted%20an%20international%20racket%20supplying%20organic%20cannabis%2C%20California%20weed%2C%20original%20gangster%20(OG)%20marijuana%2C%20and%20MDMA%20crystals%20to%20school%20and%20college%20students%20in%20Delhi-NCR.%20Six%20alleged%20traffickers%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20and%20the%20syndicate%20was%20bringing%20in%20the%20contraband%20from%20Thailand%20via%20Manipur.%20The%20suppliers%20were%20in%20contact%20with%20their%20clients%20through%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Facebook.%20The%20accused%20were%20identified%20as%20Nongmaitham%20Jashobanta%20Singh%2C%20Thiyam%20Rabikanta%20Singh%2C%20Rudransh%20Gupta%2C%20Lakshay%20Bhatia%2C%20Girik%20Aggarwal%2C%20and%20Khalid%20Zafar.%20They%20supplied%20drugs%20to%20students%20and%20had%20connections%20with%20well-known%20colleges%20and%20universities.%20Another%20operation%20in%20Kanpur%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20three%20people%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20organic%20ganja%20and%20MDMA%20in%20Delhi-NCR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAKSHI%20CHAND%20AND%20RAJSHEKHAR%20JHA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Progressives%20Need%20To%20Stop%20Hectoring%20the%20INDIA%20Parties%20on%20What%20They%20Did%20and%20Did%20Not%20Do%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20(INC)%20is%20accused%20of%20snatching%20defeat%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20many%20pre-election%20surveys%20suggested%20the%20party%20had%20a%20realistic%20chance%20of%20winning.%20In%20speculating%20on%20specific%20reasons%2C%20it%20has%20been%20argued%20that%20the%20INC%20did%20not%20give%20sufficient%20space%20to%20partners%20in%20the%20Indian%20National%20Development%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%20It%20has%20also%20been%20posited%20that%20the%20party%20did%20not%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20EVM%20tampering%2Fhacking%20seriously%20enough.%20Some%20others%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20party%20lacked%20in%20communicating%20a%20grand%20vision.%20And%20finally%2C%20some%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20organisation%20is%20inadequate%20to%20outmanoeuvre%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20machinery%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20beset%20with%20factionalism%2C%20poor%20coordination%20between%20the%20central%20and%20state%20units%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20booth-level%20presence%2C%20did%20not%20empower%20its%20grassroots%20workers%20and%20made%20mistakes%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20these%20reasons%20explain%20one%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20truth.%20Yet%2C%20every%20party%20(including%20the%20BJP)%20is%20afflicted%20with%20these%20problems.%20Plus%20none%20of%20these%20sufficiently%20explain%20the%20results.%20It%20is%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20progressive%20forces%20across%20India%20see%20the%20INC%20as%20the%20key%20fulcrum%20in%20any%20opposition%20against%20the%20BJP.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20legitimately%20feel%20frustrated%20that%20the%20party%20faltered.%20But%20we%20all%20need%20to%20concede%20that%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20was%20genuinely%20in%20the%20fight.%20Nearly%20every%20pollster%2C%20analyst%2C%20journalist%20and%20conscientious%20bystander%20sincerely%20felt%20that%20the%20INC%20was%20winning%20at%20least%20three%20(and%20maybe%20even%20four)%20of%20the%20five%20state%20elections.%20Imagine%20the%20kind%20of%20organisational%20restructuring%20and%20programmatic%20recalibration%20that%20must%20have%20been%20effected%20within%20the%20INC%20for%20it%20to%20come%20so%20far.%20Although%20it%E2%80%99s%20poor%20consolation%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3Edifference%20in%20vote%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20at%20least%20four%20states%20proves%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20both%20invested%20and%20capable%20of%20a%20spirited%20fight.%20Yes%2C%20it%20can%20(and%20must)%20do%20more%20to%20redress%20internal%20faultiness%20%E2%80%93%20simply%20because%20while%20the%20BJP%20can%20afford%20to%20make%20many%20mistakes%2C%20progressive%20forces%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20make%20even%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3EThe%20Myth%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hat-Trick%20and%20What%20the%20Statistics%20Really%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20having%20said%20that%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20we%20objectively%20understand%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20so%20we%20can%20course-correct.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20normal%20fight%20or%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20governing%20instruments%20of%20the%20state%20are%20being%20systematically%20deployed%20against%20the%20opposition.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%20(and%20equally%20crucially)%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20politically%20complemented%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20360-degree%20stratagems.%20Leveraging%20films%2C%20serials%2C%20media%2C%20social%20media%2C%20books%2C%20comics%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20organisations%2C%20social%20organisations%20etc.%2C%20they%20consistently%20outmanoeuvre%20party%20organisations%20that%20unfortunately%20still%20limit%20themselves%20to%20elections.%20The%20bitter%20truth%20is%20that%20Indians%20perceive%20such%20electoral%20engagement%20as%20transactional%20(and%20therefore%20deal%20with%20them%20instrumentally).%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Sangh%20focuses%20on%20building%20non-political%20relationships%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20consistently%20leverages%20for%20electoral%20purposes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProgressive%20forces%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethese%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20new%20frontiers%20of%20politics%20that%20they%20can%20contribute%20to.%20If%20we%20truly%20care%20about%20saving%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20we%20need%20to%20stop%20hectoring%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20on%20what%20they%20did%20and%20did%20not%20do.%20Let%20us%20leave%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20of%20electioneering%20to%20the%20professionals.%20Progressive%20parties%20like%20the%20Congress%20are%20doing%20their%20best%2C%20with%20the%20limited%20resources%20they%20have.%20Yes%2C%20they%20can%20do%20more%20to%20remedy%20structural%20problems%20(both%20within%20and%20without).%20But%20we%20progressives%20need%20to%20desist%20from%20attributing%20these%20narrow%20losses%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20not%20paying%20heed%20to%20our%20pet%20agendas.%20No%20matter%20how%20crucial%20that%20agenda%20may%20be%20to%20India%2C%20in%20pursuing%20such%20lines%20of%20argumentation%2C%20we%20are%20reflexively%20damaging%20the%20larger%20cause%20that%20all%20progressives%20are%20uniting%20for%20today.%20In%20this%20spirit%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20reflecting%20on%20what%20we%20can%20collectively%20do%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20rather%20than%20frittering%20away%20time%20in%20finger-pointing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20we%20need%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20goalposts%20of%20welfare%20politics%20have%20changed%20drastically.%20Even%20though%20some%20progressives%20would%20like%20to%20devote%20time%20and%20resources%20to%20forging%20inspiring%20documents%20detailing%20innovative%20policy%20ideas%20for%20party%20manifestos%2C%20these%20no%20longer%20shift%20electorates%20the%20way%20they%20once%20did.%20The%20nature%20of%20political%20consumption%20has%20changed%2C%20as%20has%20the%20nature%20of%20campaigning.%20Parties%20are%20resorting%20to%20competitive%20welfarism%20because%20that%20is%20what%20works.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20more%20parties%20offer%2C%20the%20muddier%20their%20message%20is%20perceived%20to%20be.%20So%20parties%20increasingly%20focus%20on%20a%20few%20select%20promises%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20and%20complement%20those%20with%20customised%20constituency-level%20promises.%20We%20can%20continue%20to%20harbour%20the%20illusion%20that%20progressive%20parties%20are%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20people%2C%20and%20keep%20proffering%20suggestions%20that%20address%20macro-level%20needs%20and%20aspirations.%20Or%20we%20can%20accept%20that%20parties%20are%20infinitely%20better%20suited%20to%20understand%20local%20issues%2C%20and%20help%20them%20connect%20with%20those%20networks%20that%20are%20even%20better%20connected%20to%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20caveat%20is%20necessary%20here.%20Competitive%20welfarism%20has%20also%20become%20just%20an%20eligibility%20criterion%20to%20stay%20relevant%20in%20electoral%20races.%20Quickly%20adapting%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-decentralised-political-process-congress-success%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20proffers%20its%20own%20version%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20nullify%20the%20propagandic%20effect%20of%20INC%E2%80%99s%20schemes.%20Consequently%2C%20promises%20(or%20delivery)%20of%20welfare%20programmes%20do%20not%20sway%20mass%20consciousness.%20To%20therefore%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20issues%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eroti-kapda-makan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadak-bijli-paani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaan-jahan-jeevika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20counterproductive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687555%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20being%20greeted%20by%20party%20workers.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BJP4India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20what%20we%20now%20need%20to%20accept%20is%20that%20today%20India%20is%20in%20an%20ideological%20era.%20Today%2C%20the%20BJP%20offers%20three%20things%20to%20the%20electorate%3A%20a)%20material%20benefits%20for%20the%20family%2Findividual%20(welfare%20schemes%20and%20promises)%3B%20b)%20enhancing%20national%20pride%20(through%20symbolic%20mega-summits%20like%20the%20G-20%2C%20alleged%20assassinations%20in%20foreign%20nations%2C%20the%20projection%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20global%20leaders%20etc.)%3B%20and%20c)%20the%20promotion%2Fprotection%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHinduism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(through%20performative%20religiosity%2C%20attacks%20on%20minority%20symbols%20etc.).%20This%20heady%20combination%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eraashtravaad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(nationalism)%20cannot%20be%20countered%20only%20by%20welfarism.%20Nor%20can%20it%20be%20countered%20by%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbehind-congress-defeat-madhya-pradesh-kamal-nath-rejection%5C%22%3Esoft%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20which%20is%20what%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20state%20leadership%20tried%20in%20vain%20in%20two%20states.%20The%20BJP%20cannot%20be%20punched%20from%20the%20right%20because%20the%20electorate%20will%20always%20choose%20the%20original.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-what-the-congress-must-do-now-to-quickly-reset-the-2024-chessboard%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20What%20the%20Congress%20Must%20Do%20Now%20to%20Quickly%20Reset%20the%202024%20Chessboard%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20Congress%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20aggressively%20project%20its%20own%20ideological%20vision%20%E2%80%93%20something%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20doing%20by%20unequivocally%20standing%20up%20for%20secularism%2C%20liberalism%2C%20democratic%20norms%2C%20nationalism%20and%20development.%20But%20INC%20needs%20to%20also%20breathe%20life%20into%20its%20vision%20by%20putting%20programmatic%20muscle%20behind%20it.%20What%20the%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20unleash%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Freengineering-indias-consciousness%2Farticle65712443.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehundred%20ideological%20projects%20across%20the%20nation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(which%20will%20undoubtedly%20help%20the%20entire%20INDIA%20bloc).%20And%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20non-political%20progressive%20forces%20can%20make%20a%20substantive%20contribution%20to%20further%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20promise.%20These%20ideological%20projects%20are%20not%20just%20to%20reshape%20mass%20consciousness%20but%20also%20to%20forge%20fresh%20relationships%20with%20the%20people.%20The%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(BJY)%20was%20one%20such%20initiative%2C%20which%20reconnected%20progressives%20across%20India%20with%20the%20INC.%20But%20to%20be%20effective%2C%20many%20more%20projects%20will%20need%20to%20be%20spearheaded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20progressives%20need%20a%20galaxy%20of%20projects%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20sub-caste%20Dalits%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20and%20Adivasis%20on%20a%20socio-cultural%20level.%20The%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20undoubtedly%20beginning%20to%20re-engineer%20their%20party%20structures%20(for%20example%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdkplc2mbj%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fv1695636030%2FText_Congress_Consitution_English_15_July_2023_Final_4b6c600ed6.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%20VI-A%20and%20B%20of%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20constitution%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20recently%20amended%20at%20its%20Raipur%20plenary%20to%20reserve%2050%25%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20%5BSCs%5D%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20%5BSTs%5D%2C%20OBCs%2C%20women%2C%20and%20minorities).%20They%20are%20also%20proposing%20to%20deepen%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20justice%20paradigm%20to%20inspire%20historically%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society%20(most%20notably%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20caste%20census).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20these%20are%20not%20nearly%20enough%2C%20given%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20not%20only%20appropriates%20SC-ST-OBC%20icons%20but%20also%20celebrates%20their%20festivals%20while%20giving%20sub-castes%20political%20representation.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-caste-survey-politics-is-obc-vote-eluding-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAxis%20My%20India%20poll%20shows%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20enjoyed%20a%2026%25-point%20lead%20among%20the%20OBCs%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%2024%25-point%20lead%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20a%2013%25-point%20lead%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20The%20election-oriented%20organisations%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20need%20help%20in%20programmatically%20countering%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20designs%20(which%20are%20designed%20to%20capture%20hearts%20and%20minds%20while%20injecting%20communal%2C%20casteist%2C%20illiberal%20and%20undemocratic%20values).%20This%20is%20where%20progressives%20can%20tangibly%20help.%20Instead%20of%20just%20amplifying%20their%20issues%20in%20the%20media%2Fsocial%20media%20or%20even%20in%20parliament%2C%20it%20would%20be%20infinitely%20more%20meaningful%20if%20we%20put%20boots%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20progressives%20can%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fan-open-letter-to-the-indian-film-industry%2Farticle66337866.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einsert%20liberal%2C%20secular%20and%20democratic%20values%20in%20films%20and%20serials%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(instead%20of%20limiting%20themselves%20to%20clandestinely%20suggesting%20campaign%20slogans%20and%20limericks%2C%20which%20even%20professional%20advertising%20agencies%20can%20be%20hired%20to%20do).%20Progressives%20can%20also%20work%20at%20the%20grassroots%20with%20Adivasi%20communities%20(to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20weaving%20away%20Adivasis%20away%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20these%20state%20elections).%20Progressives%20can%20also%20work%20to%20mobilise%20women%20through%20constructive%20work%20and%20cultural%20programmes%20(to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDurga%20Vahini%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahila%20Morcha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20were%20instrumental%20in%20ensuring%20women%20became%20a%20voting%20bloc%20for%20the%20BJP).%20Likewise%2C%20civil%20society%20can%20coordinate%20within%20themselves%20to%20mobilise%20sub-district%20level%20progressives%20for%20a%20plethora%20of%20community-based%20socio-cultural%20programmes.%20Diaspora%20progressives%20can%20similarly%20mobilise%20progressives%20in%20every%20nation%2C%20both%20to%20support%20progressive%20causes%20in%20India%20and%20to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20BJP.%20And%20finally%2C%20instead%20of%20symbolic%20and%20theatric%20pietism%20before%20elections%2C%20it%20would%20be%20expedient%20to%20spearhead%20a%20pan-India%20initiative%20to%20reclaim%20and%20reform%20Hinduism%20by%20working%20with%20its%20more%20progressive%20stakeholders%20(temple%20trusts%2C%20societies%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakharas%2Fmaths%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20etc.%2C%20which%20are%20simmering%20at%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20for%20appropriating%20their%20functions).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThirdly%2C%20for%20this%20plan%20to%20succeed%2C%20all%20INDIA%20parties%20(from%20the%20national%20to%20the%20district%20level)%20need%20to%20back%20such%20ideological%20projects%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20Of%20course%2C%20such%20ideological%20projects%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emust%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20perforce%20be%20delinked%20from%20elections%20and%20the%20party%20organisations.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20always%20be%20sacrificed%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20political%20exigencies.%20However%2C%20if%20this%20can%20be%20fructified%2C%20we%20recreate%20the%20Congress%20Movement%20(an%20INDIA-Movement%20if%20I%20may)%20that%20transcends%20partisan%20lines%20and%20gives%20an%20actual%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etakkar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(counter)%20to%20the%20Sangh%20parivar.%20This%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ramping%20up%20last-mile%20connectivity%20(which%20is%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20an%20upper%20hand%2C%20since%20it%20is%20able%20to%20convert%20waves%20into%20votes).%20It%20will%20also%20act%20as%20a%20feedback%20mechanism%20for%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20(which%20is%20sorely%20needed%20especially%20for%20the%20national%20parties%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20state%20units%20for%20feedback.%20This%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20given%20state%20units%20are%20averse%20to%20passing%20on%20any%20feedback%20that%20disrupts%20the%20status%20quo).%20And%20most%20importantly%2C%20like%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20it%20will%20constructively%20channelise%20every%20patriot%20in%20the%20defence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJoint%20opposition%20parties%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40kharge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20this%20requires%20progressive%20parties%20to%20both%20unlearn%20and%20relearn%20some%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20they%20need%20to%20accept%20the%20limitations%20of%20creating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%2C%20mahol%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a%20narrative%20wave)%20to%20win%20elections.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20in%20creating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20parties%20outsource%20key%20political%20functions%20to%20external%20agencies%20(crippling%20parties%20structurally%20and%20diverting%20scarce%20resources).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20given%20its%20disproportionate%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20chokehold%20on%20the%20media%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20better%20placed%20at%20generating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20resource-intensive%20method%20of%20campaigning%20also%20makes%20parties%20more%20susceptible%20to%20diverting%20resources%20from%20pro-people%20schemes%20when%20in%20government%20(which%20is%20what%20led%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20in%20Karnataka).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20progressive%20parties%20also%20need%20to%20stop%20relying%20on%20demagogues%20to%20enthuse%20electorates.%20Demagogues%20can%20temporarily%20enthral%2C%20but%20that%20rapture%20is%20limited%20to%20the%20length%20of%20the%20programme%20they%E2%80%99re%20speaking%20in.%20They%20do%20nothing%20to%20truly%20influence%20minds%20or%20convert%20them%20into%20votes.%20What%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20really%20need%20today%20and%20tomorrow%20is%20a%20veritable%20army%20of%20progressive%20evangelicals%2C%20who%20work%20consistently%20and%20silently%2C%20away%20from%20the%20media-glare.%20These%20evangelicals%20(and%20the%20ideological%20projects)%20they%20will%20spearhead%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20silver%20bullet%20to%20outmatch%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20and%20the%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eamrit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20reclaim%20the%20hearts%20and%20minds%20of%20our%20people.%20Creating%20this%20institutionalised%20network%20of%20ideological%20projects%20will%20take%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20how%20long%20can%20we%20keep%20bandaging%20something%20that%20clearly%20needs%20surgery%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpushparaj-deshpande%5C%22%3EPushparaj%20Deshpande%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Samruddha%20Bharat%20Foundation%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3ERethinking%20India%3Cem%3E%20series%20(Penguin).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701916254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprogressives-stop-hectoring-india-parties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20India's%20constitution%20should%20leave%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20of%20electioneering%20to%20the%20professionals.%20It%20is%20worth%20reflecting%20on%20what%20can%20be%20collectively%20done%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20rather%20than%20frittering%20away%20time%20in%20finger-pointing.%20%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprogressives-stop-hectoring-india-parties%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20grounds%20entire%20Osprey%20fleet%20after%20fatal%20crash%20in%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701915906000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0E83%2Fproduction%2F_115651730_breaking-promo-976.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67645072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20comes%20after%20eight%20service%20members%20died%20in%20a%20crash%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Japan%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A450%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67645072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67645072.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67645072.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Received%20call%20from%20Rahul%2C%20INDIA%20partners%20will%20meet%20soon%3A%20Didi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701915885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105796392%2Cimgsize-854787.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fhad-received-call-from-rahul-india-partners-will-meet-soon-mamata-banerjee%2Farticleshow%2F105796378.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20CM%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20confirms%20that%20she%20will%20meet%20with%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20soon%20after%20receiving%20a%20call%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20The%20scheduled%20meeting%20was%20cancelled%20due%20to%20Banerjee's%20trip%20to%20north%20Bengal%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20illness%2C%20and%20M%20K%20Stalin's%20involvement%20in%20flood%20relief%20efforts%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Banerjee%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20meeting%20but%20expressed%20little%20concern%20about%20the%20delay.%20She%20plans%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20in%20the%20third%20week%20of%20December.%20Banerjee%20acknowledges%20that%20it%20was%20understandable%20for%20Stalin%20to%20be%20unable%20to%20attend%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20floods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DWAIPAYAN%20GHOSH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fhad-received-call-from-rahul-india-partners-will-meet-soon-mamata-banerjee%2Farticleshow%2F105796378.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Noam%20Chomsky%20at%2095%3A%20One%20of%20the%20Greatest%20Living%20Challengers%20of%20Unjust%20Power%20and%20Delusions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F27102320%2Fnoam-chomsky.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20December%207%2C%20is%20Noam%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%2095th%20birth%20anniversary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20introduction%20to%20his%201969%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EAmerican%20Power%20and%20the%20New%20Mandarins%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ENoam%20Chomsky%20cites%20a%20news%20item%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20York%20Times%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20March%2018%2C%201968%20captioned%20%E2%80%98Army%20Exhibit%20Bars%20Shooting%20at%20Vietnamese%20Hut%E2%80%99.%20The%20news%20item%2C%20Chomsky%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9Creports%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98peace%20movement%E2%80%99%20to%20disrupt%20an%20exhibit%20in%20the%20Chicago%20Museum%20of%20Science%20and%20Industry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBeginning%20today%2C%20visitors%20can%20no%20longer%20enter%20a%20helicopter%20for%20simulated%20firing%20of%20a%20machine%20gun%20at%20targets%20in%20a%20diorama%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20Central%20Highlands.%20The%20targets%20were%20a%20hut%2C%20two%20bridges%20and%20an%20ammunition%20dump%2C%20and%20a%20light%20flashed%20when%20a%20hit%20was%20scored%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CApparently%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chomsky%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20great%20fun%20for%20the%20kiddies%20until%20those%20damned%20peaceniks%20turned%20up%20and%20started%20one%20of%20their%20interminable%20demonstrations%E2%80%A6.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%2C%20%E2%80%98demonstrators%20particularly%20objected%20to%20children%20being%20permitted%20to%20%E2%80%98fire%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20hut%2C%20even%20though%20no%20people%20appear%20there%20or%20elsewhere%20on%20the%20diorama%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20just%20shows%20how%20unreasonable%20peaceniks%20can%20be.%20Although%20it%20is%20small%20compensation%20for%20the%20closing%20of%20this%20entertaining%20exhibit%2C%20(the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20adds)%2C%20%E2%80%98visitors%20can%20still%20test%20their%20skills%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20exhibition%20by%20simulated%20firing%20of%20an%20antitank%20weapon%20and%20several%20models%20of%20rifles%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20next%20paragraph%2C%20Chomsky%20goes%20on%20thus%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20one%20say%20about%20a%20country%20where%20a%20museum%20of%20science%20in%20a%20great%20city%20can%20feature%20an%20exhibit%20in%20which%20people%20fire%20machine%20guns%20at%20Vietnamese%20huts%2C%20with%20a%20light%20flashing%20when%20a%20hit%20is%20scored%3F%20What%20can%20one%20say%20about%20a%20country%20where%20such%20an%20idea%20can%20even%20be%20considered%3F%20You%20have%20to%20weep%20for%20this%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20written%20at%20the%20height%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20Noam%20Chomsky%2C%20aged%2039%2C%20was%20already%20a%20veteran%20of%20the%20country-wide%20protests%20against%20that%20war%2C%20campaigning%20on%20university%20campuses%20including%20at%20Harvard%20and%20Berkley%2C%20leading%20an%20electrifying%20anti-war%20teach-in%20just%20outside%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20participating%20in%20civil%20disobedience%20movements%20and%20marching%20on%20Washington%20DC%20along%20with%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20others%20to%20%E2%80%98return%E2%80%99%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20(army)%20%E2%80%98draft%20cards%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General%E2%80%99s%20office.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehomsky%2C%20a%20tenured%20full%20professor%20at%20MIT%20since%20he%20was%2032%2C%20had%20already%20been%20imprisoned%20several%20times%2C%20and%20was%20detained%20again%20in%20October%201967%20after%20that%20historic%20Pentagon%20demonstration.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20happened%20to%20share%20his%20prison%20cell%20with%20the%20novelist%20Norman%20Mailer%20who%2C%20in%20his%20classic%20account%20of%20this%20stirring%20moment%20in%20American%20history%20%E2%80%93%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Armies%20of%20the%20Night%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Edescribed%20his%20cell-mate%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20slim%2C%20sharp-featured%20man%20with%20an%20ascetic%20expression%20and%20an%20air%20of%20gentle%20but%20absolute%20moral%20authority%E2%80%9D%2C%20seemed%20%E2%80%9Cuneasy%20at%20the%20thought%20of%20missing%20class%20on%20Monday%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20308px)%2085vw%2C%20308px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06154752%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22308%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06154752%2Funnamed.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06154752%2Funnamed-199x300.jpg%20199w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22463%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENormal%20Mailer%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Armies%20of%20the%20Night%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ENew%20American%20Library%20(1968).%20The%20cover%20page%20shows%20Noam%20Chomsky%20(second%20from%20left)%20among%20other%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20given%20many%20years%20later%2C%20for%20the%202006%20documentary%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EChildren%20of%20Armageddon%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EChomsky%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20remembered%20the%20day%20news%20of%20the%20Hiroshima%20bombing%20broke%20in%20the%20US.%20Chomsky%20replied%20%E2%80%98Yes%2C%20quite%20well%E2%80%99%2C%20whereupon%20the%20interviewer%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20he%20recalled%20how%20he%20had%20reacted%20to%20it.%20Chomsky%20hesitated%20a%20little%20%E2%80%93%20clearly%2C%20the%20memory%20was%20still%20a%20very%20disquieting%20one%20%E2%80%93%20before%20he%20confessed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CDoubly%20shocked%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added%2C%20by%20the%20sheer%20savagery%20of%20the%20act%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20equally%2C%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20absence%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eany%20reaction%20to%20it%E2%80%9D%20around%20him.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20aged%2016%2C%20he%20had%20just%20graduated%20from%20high%20school%20and%20was%20on%20a%20summer%20camp.%20As%20the%20news%20came%20in%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cit%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20make%20any%20difference%20to%20anybody%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20remember%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20talk%20to%20anyone.%20There%20was%20nobody.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stay%20where%20I%20was.%20I%20just%20walked%20off%20by%20myself%20to%20somewhere%20in%20the%20woods%20and%20stayed%20there%20for%20maybe%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%E2%80%A6..%20till%20it%20was%20getting%20dark.%20%E2%80%A6I%20felt%20completely%20isolated%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChomsky%20then%20recounted%20an%20episode%20from%20several%20years%20later%2C%20possibly%20the%20early%201950s%2C%20when%20information%20about%20the%20horrors%20of%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20was%20still%20widely%20censored%20in%20the%20US.%20One%20evening%20in%20Boston%2C%20Chomsky%20and%20his%20wife%20felt%20like%20watching%20a%20movie.%20They%20scanned%20the%20movie%20pages%20of%20the%20local%20newspaper%20to%20decide%20which%20film%20to%20see%2C%20and%20were%20surprised%20to%20find%20a%20film%20called%20%E2%80%98Hiroshima%E2%80%99%20billed%20at%20a%20downtown%20Boston%20theatre%20located%20in%20Boston%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Redlight%E2%80%99%20district%20(so%20called%20because%20the%20neighbourhood%20mostly%20featured%20pornographic%20movies).%20The%20Chomskys%20were%20keen%20to%20check%20the%20film%20out%20and%20went.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20turned%20out%20that%20it%20was%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20poorly-made%20documentary%20film%20but%20it%20contained%20graphic%20images%20of%20the%20carnage%20of%20August%206%2C%201945%2C%20obviously%20filmed%20on-site%20at%20Hiroshima%20on%2C%20and%20immediately%20after%2C%20that%20dreadful%20day.%20There%20were%20pictures%20of%20appalling%20devastation%2C%20of%20people%20with%20their%20skin%20falling%20off%20their%20bodies%2C%20screaming%20and%20running%20towards%20the%20river%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20salving%20their%20wounds.%20And%2C%20Chomsky%20recalled%20with%20a%20perceptible%20shudder%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20in%20the%20audience%20were%20laughing%E2%80%A6%20laughing..%20They%20perhaps%20took%20it%20for%20a%20pornographic%20movie%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20One%20can%20actually%20hear%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20voice%20trail%20off%20as%20he%20remembers%20that%20day%20on%20camera.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChomsky%E2%80%99s%20moral%20universe%20had%20been%20shaped%2C%20by%20his%20own%20account%2C%20%E2%80%9Cby%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%201930s%2C%20by%20the%20war%20in%20Ethiopia%2C%20the%20Russian%20purges%2C%20the%20China%20incident%2C%20the%20Spanish%20Civil%20War%2C%20the%20Nazi%20atrocities%2C%20the%20Western%20reaction%20to%20these%20events%20and%2C%20in%20part%2C%20their%20complicity%20in%20them%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20The%20fall%20of%20Republican%20Barcelona%20in%20January%201939%20in%20the%20Spanish%20Civil%20War%20was%20a%20watershed%20in%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20persuaded%2010-year-old%20Noam%20to%20write%2C%20for%20his%20school%20magazine%2C%20his%20first%20published%20article.%20Even%20though%20he%20had%20taken%20up%20theoretical%20linguistics%20partly%20fortuitously%2C%20Chomsky%20was%20to%20eventually%20emerge%20as%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E-century%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20language%20theorist%2Fphilosopher%20whose%20work%20has%20profoundly%20influenced%20education%20theory%2C%20psychology%2C%20psycholinguistics%2C%20neurolinguistics%2C%C2%A0%20computational%20theory%20and%20computer%20learning%20as%20well%20as%20cognitive%20science%20in%20general.%20He%20pioneered%20the%20cognitivist%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20then%20widely%20popular%20behaviourist%2C%20approach%20to%20language%20theory%2C%20and%20established%20its%20preeminence%20among%20the%20competing%20epistemological%20systems%20of%20human%20language.%20And%2C%20in%20a%20very%20real%20sense%2C%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20path-breaking%20work%20in%20language%20theory%20also%20links%20up%20with%20the%20fundamental%20moral%20concerns%20that%20have%20informed%20all%20his%20adult%20years%3A%20human%20dignity%2C%20equality%2C%20social%20justice%20and%20freedom.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20he%20once%20said%20about%20the%20linkages%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F5599576288_6d200ac24c_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F5599576288_6d200ac24c_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F5599576288_6d200ac24c_b-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F5599576288_6d200ac24c_b-768x512.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-88391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENoam%20Chomsky.%20Photo%3A%20Andrew%20Rusk%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%202.0%2C%20Marc%20Lozano%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20intensive%20study%20of%20one%20aspect%20of%20human%20psychology%20%E2%80%93%20human%20language%20%E2%80%93%20may%20contribute%20to%20a%20humanistic%20social%20science%20that%20will%20serve%20as%20well%20as%20an%20instrument%20for%20social%20action.%20It%20must%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20be%20stressed%20that%20social%20action%20cannot%20await%20a%20firmly%20established%20theory%20of%20man%20and%20society%2C%20nor%20can%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20latter%20be%20determined%20by%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehopes%20and%20moral%20judgements.%20The%20two%20%E2%80%93%20speculation%20and%20action%20%E2%80%93%20must%20progress%20as%20best%20they%20can%2C%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20day%20when%20theoretical%20enquiry%20will%20provide%20a%20firm%20guide%20to%20the%20unending%2C%20often%20grim%2C%20but%20never%20hopeless%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20and%20social%20justice.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(From%20the%20essay%20%3C%2Fspan%3ELanguage%20and%20Freedom%3Cb%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Eoriginally%20a%20lecture%20given%20at%20Loyola%20University%2C%20Chicago%20in%20January%201970)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20does%20Chomsky%20believe%20that%20the%20study%20of%20the%20humans%E2%80%99%20facility%20for%20language%20can%20open%20the%20door%20for%20meaningful%20social%20action%3F%20A%20clue%20to%20the%20answer%20probably%20lies%20in%20another%20part%20of%20the%20same%20essay%2C%20where%20he%20expands%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20freedom%20and%20creativity%20running%20through%20man%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20language%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLanguage%20is%20a%20process%20of%20free%20creation%3B%20its%20laws%20and%20principles%20are%20fixed%2C%20but%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20principles%20of%20generation%20are%20used%20is%20free%20and%20infinitely%20varied.%20Even%20the%20interpretation%20and%20use%20of%20words%20involves%20a%20process%20of%20free%20creation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20implies%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20choices%2C%20and%20Chomsky%20never%20tires%20of%20reminding%20us%20that%20everyone%20needs%20to%20make%20a%20choice%20on%20a%20multiplicity%20of%20issues%20everyday%20if%20we%20are%20to%20stay%20human.%20In%20the%20%E2%80%98Q%26amp%3BA%E2%80%99%20session%20following%20a%20talk%20he%20delivered%20in%20the%20Asian%20School%20of%20Journalism%20in%20Chennai%20in%20October%202001%2C%20a%20budding%20journalist%20asked%20Chomsky%20if%20he%20was%20not%20being%20%E2%80%98too%20optimistic%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20world%20that%20otherwise%20looked%20quite%20bleak.%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20reply%20was%20simple%2C%20almost%20matter-of-fact%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20measure%20of%20how%20optimistic%20you%20ought%20to%20be.%20In%20fact%2C%20as%20far%20as%20optimism%20is%20concerned%2C%20you%20basically%20have%20two%20choices.%20You%20can%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Nothing%20is%20going%20to%20work%20and%20so%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20do%20anything.%E2%80%99%20You%20can%20therefore%20guarantee%20that%20the%20worst%20possible%20outcome%20will%20come%20about.%20Or%20you%20can%20take%20the%20other%20option%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Maybe%20something%20will%20work%20and%20I%20will%20engage%20myself%20in%20trying%20to%C2%A0%20make%20it%20work.%20Maybe%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20things%20will%20get%20better%E2%80%99.%20That%20is%20your%20choice.%20Nobody%20can%20tell%20you%20how%20right%20it%20is%20to%20be%20optimistic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20329px)%2085vw%2C%20329px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F29123746%2Frequiem-for-the.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22329%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F29123746%2Frequiem-for-the.jpg%20401w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F29123746%2Frequiem-for-the-241x300.jpg%20241w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333848%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERequiem%20for%20the%20American%20Dream%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ENoam%20Chomsky%3Cbr%3ESeven%20Stories%20Press%20(2017)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20hint%20of%20high%20passion%20here%2C%20for%20Chomsky%20clearly%20thinks%20he%20is%20only%20stating%20the%20obvious.%20But%20he%20also%20knows%20that%2C%20sometimes%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20the%20obvious%2C%20at%20any%20rate%20not%20for%20the%20modern-day%20intellectual.%20As%20far%20back%20as%20June%2C%201966%2C%20while%20delivering%20at%20Harvard%2C%20in%20an%20anti-Vietnam%20War%20rally%2C%20what%20proved%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%E2%80%99s%20great%20speeches%2C%20he%20had%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20intellectuals%20to%20speak%20the%20truth%20and%20to%20expose%20lies.%20This%2C%20at%20least%2C%20seems%20enough%20of%20a%20truism%20to%20pass%20without%20comment.%20Not%20so%2C%20however.%20For%20the%20modern%20intellectual%2C%20it%20is%20not%20at%20all%20obvious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Chomsky%2C%20however%2C%20this%20responsibility%20was%20always%20axiomatic.%20For%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20side%20of%20successive%20US%20administrations%2C%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%2C%20for%20his%20incisive%2C%20insistent%20probing%20of%20the%20real%20drivers%20of%20American%20foreign%20policy.%20His%20unblinking%20gaze%20on%20how%20the%20US%20propped%20up%20the%20most%20brutal%20regimes%20in%20Nicaragua%2C%20El%20Salvadore%2C%20Guatemala%20and%20Chile%20through%20the%201970s%20earned%20him%20a%20place%20on%20President%20Nixon%E2%80%99s%20infamous%20%E2%80%98Enemies%20List%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20recognised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20chief%20architects%20of%20the%20independence%20of%20East%20Timor.%20By%20insistently%2C%20even%20stridently%2C%20raising%20his%20voice%20against%20unspeakable%2C%20US-aided%20Indonesian%20atrocities%20against%20the%20East%20Timorese%2C%20he%20had%20helped%20focus%20international%20public%20opinion%20on%20East%20Timor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202002%2C%C2%A0%20he%20appeared%20unsolicited%20at%20an%20Istanbul%20court%20to%20plead%20that%20he%20be%20made%20a%20co-accused%20in%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriminal%20prosecution%20involving%20Fatih%20Tas%2C%20an%20important%20Turkish%20publisher.%20Tas%20had%20published%20a%20Turkish%20translation%20of%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EAmerican%20Interventionism%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20book%20of%20essays%20highlighting%20the%20Turkish%20government%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20persecution%20of%20Turkiye%E2%80%99s%20Kurdish%20population%20with%20American%20support.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20amused%2C%20the%20Turkish%20State%20was%20prosecuting%20Tas%20for%20%E2%80%98producing%20propaganda%20against%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20dismayed%2C%20however%2C%20by%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20appearance%20in%20Turkiye%20and%20his%20plea%20to%20be%20tried%20alongside%20Tas.%20All%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20media%20had%20got%20wind%20of%20the%20professor%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20country%20and%20were%20sure%20to%20turn%20up%20in%20strength%20to%20report%20on%20the%20court%20proceedings%20live.%20The%20Turkish%20authorities%20panicked%20and%20dropped%20the%20prosecution%2C%20saving%20the%20publisher%20from%20a%20certain%20prison%20sentence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChomsky%E2%80%99s%20reaction%20was%20characteristically%20understated.%20Because%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20US%20provides%2080%25%20of%20the%20arms%20for%20Turkiye%20for%20the%20express%20purpose%20of%20carrying%20out%20repression%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20felt%20it%20was%20his%20duty%2C%20as%20a%20US%20citizen%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20Turkiye%E2%80%99s%20human%20rights%20abuses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20like%20me%20who%20have%20followed%20and%20admired%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20work%20for%20decades%2C%20it%20is%20unsurprising%20%E2%80%93%20because%20for%20him%20it%20is%20second%20nature%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20always%20downplays%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20own%20interventions%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20critical%20questions%20our%20world%20is%20confronted%20with%3A%20war%20and%20peace%2C%20egregious%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20powerful%20States%2C%20the%20plunder%20of%20the%20commons%20by%20transnational%20corporations%2C%20the%20depredations%20of%20finance%20capital%2C%20and%20the%20ever-lengthening%20shadow%20of%20ecological%20disaster.%20And%20yet%20one%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20but%20marvel%20at%20Chomsky%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20a%20question%20that%20Al%20Jazeera%20asked%20him%20in%20April%20this%20year%20in%20course%20of%20an%20interview.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20that%20tete-a%E2%80%99-tete%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAJ%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EFew%20intellectuals%20have%20caused%20greater%20controversy%20than%20yourself.%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20regrets%20for%20any%20of%20the%20positions%20that%20you%20have%20taken%20or%20not%20taken%20related%20to%20your%20advocacy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENC%3Ci%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20having%20not%20taken%2C%20yes.%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20retract%20those%20I%20have%20taken%2C%20but%20there%20are%20many%20things%20I%20should%20have%20done%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%E2%80%A6..%20I%20became%20quite%20active%20in%20opposing%20the%20(Vietnam)%20war%20in%20the%20early%201960s%E2%80%A6%20but%20that%20was%20too%20late.%20Should%20have%20been%2010%20years%20earlier%20when%20the%20US%20began%20to%20support%20the%20French%20effort%20to%20reconquer%20their%20former%20colony%20and%2C%20when%20the%20French%20failed%2C%20the%20US%20took%20over%2C%20undermined%20the%20Geneva%20Accords%2C%20established%20a%20client%20state%20in%20the%20south%20that%20killed%2060%20or%2070%20thousand%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20protest%20should%20have%20begun.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20the%20latter%20part%20of%20the%201960s%2C%20there%20was%20no%20really%20organised%20opposition.%20That%20was%20criminal%20and%20I%20should%20have%20started%20earlier%2C%20same%20on%20other%20things%E2%80%A6.Take%20Israel%2C%20the%20leading%20issue%20of%20my%20life%20since%20early%20childhood.%20I%20started%20talking%20about%20the%20criminal%20nature%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20in%201969%20%E2%80%93%20it%20should%20have%20been%20much%20earlier.%20I%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20repression%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20in%20Israel.%20I%E2%80%99d%20seen%20it%20at%20first%20hand%E2%80%A6.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20become%20involved%20until%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9967%20war%20and%20Israel%20initiated%20its%20policies%20of%20settlement%20and%20development%20in%20the%20occupied%20territories%2C%20which%20expanded%20and%20led%20to%20the%20current%20situation.%20I%20was%20much%20too%20mild%20in%20my%20criticism%20and%20much%20too%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C(T)here%20are%20many%20things%20I%20should%20have%20done%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%E2%80%9D.%20Nobler%20words%20than%20these%20have%20seldom%20been%20heard%20in%20our%20time.%20One%20hopes%20Noam%20Chomsky%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98the%20greatest%20living%20challenger%20of%20unjust%20power%20and%20delusions%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20Edward%20Said%E2%80%99s%20memorable%20words%20%E2%80%93continues%20to%20work%20and%20teach%20us%20all%20for%20many%20more%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EAnjan%20Basu%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20basuanjan52%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701914400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F27102320%2Fnoam-chomsky.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnoam-chomsky-at-95-challenger-unjust-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrating%20the%20man%20whose%20life%20more%20than%20anyone%20else%E2%80%99s%20tells%20us%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20be%20human.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnoam-chomsky-at-95-challenger-unjust-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Masked%20Singer%E2%80%99%20Reveals%20Identity%20of%20Husky%20and%20Tiki%3A%20Here%20Are%20the%20Celebrities%20Under%20the%20Costumes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701914400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FHusky-Tiki-Masked-Singer.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235825236%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SPOILER%20ALERT%3A%20Do%20not%20read%20ahead%20if%20you%20have%20not%20watched%20Season%2010%2C%20Episode%2010%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Masked%20Singer%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CI%20Wanna%20Rock%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20aired%20Dec.%206%20on%20Fox.%20Ginuwine%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Masked%20Singer%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20first%20came%20calling.%20But%20the%20%E2%80%9CPony%E2%80%9D%20artist%20ultimately%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20resist.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%20I%20said%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietyschneider%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%